title: 240419 Workout of the Day
body:
3 rounds for time:

50 wall-ball shots

50 lateral burpee box jump-overs

 

W: 14-lb ball to a 9-foot target, 20-inch box

M: 20-lb ball to a 10-foot target, 24-inch box

 

Time cap: 20 minutes

title: 240409 Workout of the Day
body:
3 rounds for time of:

 

10 strict chest-to-bar pull-ups

20 hand-release push-ups

30 dumbbell front-rack walking lunges

 

W: 20 lb

M: 35 lb
